						<p>On another gold plated staff.</p>						

						<p>Mīnākshamma.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1656, Ānanda, Māgha Śu. 2 Tuesday</hi> corresponding <hi rend="bold">1735 A.D. January 14, Tuesday f.d.t. °17.</hi></p>						

						<p>States that the staff weighing 1658 <hi rend="italic">va.ga (Varāha gadyāṇa)</hi> and 12 <hi rend="italic">na</hi> was the gift of Kṛishṇājamma. Published; <hi rend="italic">S.I.I.,</hi> Vol. XXIV, No. 567.</p>						

